		"description": "{html}<div><p>Please create implementation tickets once this feature has been\ndesigned.</p>\n<p>JSLint is helpful in warning of potential JS issues. It should\nbe configurable in <code>tiapp.xml</code> and at least support the\nfollowing features.</p>\n<p>Configure action per mode. For example in test mode you might\nwant to continue after warnings or errors, in development mode you\nmight want to continue if warnings but not on errors, in production\nyou may want to fail on warnings and errors.</p>\n<p>See <a href=\n\"http://developer.appcelerator.com/helpdesk/view/56271\">Helpdesk\n56271</a></p></div>{html}",
